_sText:
This map is made for the NegX mapping contest. It is based  around aim_ag_texture2 and it has 60 spawn points (I believe). I have a radar and NAV file for it and also a custom skybox but due to problems I haven't incuded these on this DL right now. Though I will update the file when this is fixed.

Its base around aim_ag_texture2. I used some of the same things from the original and added some of my own. I also switched around the layout, but you can see the resemblances to the original.

TRON- skybox
fr33k- radar
zzdd- help getting it all together ^^
